Title: Wind Gust
Feature: Pushes enemies away with a powerful gust of wind.

Title: Whirlwind
Feature: Summons a whirlwind that moves across the battlefield, pushing enemies away.

Title: Updraft
Feature: Generates an updraft that boosts movement speed and allows temporary flight.

Title: Hurricane

Title: Gust
